videos.description: Destiny Slocum drives down the lane, spins and puts up a fadeaway jumper.
videos.headline: Slocum sinks fadeaway jumper

videos.description: Oregon State swing the ball around to Kat Tudor, who knocks down a corner 3-pointer.
